title: Default values are not shown in Show Report Parameters dialog
OB: Default values are not being shown in the Show Report Parameters dialog.
EB: When previewing the report and clicking the 'Show Report Parameters' button, the expected result is that the default values should be displayed in the value box. This allows the user to easily modify the parameters they want to change. However, the actual result is that when the 'Enter Parameters' dialog appears, all values are empty. This requires the user to input all values, even if they only want to modify one parameter.
